modName: Qethhe Do Fin Dovahhe - Bones Of The Dragons
summary:
DAWNGUARD REQUIRED (Non-Dawnguard version may be made)

A custom set of Dragonplate armor and adds a custom Dragonbone sword and Greatsword to your game.
descriptionHtml:
LOOKING FOR PEOPLE WHO CAN RETEXTURE THESE WEAPONS!!! I would really like for them to have custom textures, so if you are interested leave a comment or contact me via nexus

This is a mod that adds dragon based armors with custom stats to your game
 
The mod includes:

Cuirass of the Dragons
Helm of the Dragons
Gauntlets of the Dragons
Greaves of the Dragons
Shield of the Dragons
Blade of the Dragons
Longblade of the Dragons

Again, THIS MOD REQUIRES DAWNGUARD OR SKYRIM WILL CRASH! I may make a version where dawnguard is not required at some point.

Now in the Steam Workshop: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=165239326&searchtext=qethhe
author: themusician6
